wikipedia_page.main: Trevor Angove (born 15 January 1959 in Troon, Cornwall) is a former English List A cricketer who played his only List A game for Cornwall Cricket Club, in which he scored 13 and did not bowl.He also played 71 Minor Counties Championship games and 3 Minor counties trophy games for Cornwall.
